title: Net acquisition of financial assets (% of GDP)
name: gc.ast.totl.gd.zs
readme: Net acquisition of government financial assets includes domestic and foreign financial claims, SDRs, and gold bullion held by monetary authorities as a reserve asset. The net acquisition of financial assets should be offset by the net incurrence of liabilities.
